INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS**: Install: Copy the map (bsp file) and paste it into your Cstrike maps directory.
\Steam\SteamApps\Name\counter-strike source\cstrike\map

DESCRIPTION**: Meant to be play with any zombie mod. Has 3 level basement with an outside. Three buildings outside with rails and windows. 

BUGS: You may want to list any bugs here, if your mod and or file has any.

COMMENTS: Also i made sure there was enough pop mechines and chairs to be used. =)
